This app does not request or use any special permissions beyond local storage access through internal device memory.

4. Third-Party Services
Spin Maker does not use any third-party analytics, ads, or cloud services.

5. Data Retention
All entered data is stored locally on your device and remains there until you uninstall the app or manually clear the data.

